{
  "texts": [
    "For each pair of models, we generate 50 such conversations.",
    "Evaluation Metrics.",
    "We evaluate these LLMs on five metrics -(1) Agency; (2) Intentionality; (3) Motivation; (4) Self-Efficacy; (5) Self-Regulation.",
    "We apply the best-performing classification models from Section 7 to the generated dialogues to automatically measure these metrics.",
    "We report mean values with their level of significance."
  ]
}